OL,3,C'Worst nightmare' for government as
OL,4,CGreens secure first ever by-election
OL,5,Cvictory
OL,7,F"Sorry to customers who booked me in,"
OL,8,Fsaid former plumber Hannah Spencer as
OL,9,Fher party won its first ever by-
OL,10,Felection, "but I'm heading to
OL,11,FWestminster."
OL,13,FThe Greens' newest MP has pulled off a
OL,14,Fremarkable win. With nearly 15,000
OL,15,Fvotes, she was more than 5,000 ahead
OL,16,Fof Labour's Angeliki Stogia in what
OL,17,Fshould been a safe seat for the
OL,18,Fgovernment. Reform UK's candidate Matt
OL,19,FGoodwin came second, with 9,364 votes.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@fO]rD@KOUsD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
