OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772186488
OL,3,C'Worst nightmare' for government as
OL,4,CGreens secure first ever by-election
OL,5,Cvictory
OL,7,FFor the Greens, this is a historic
OL,8,Fresult. Zack Polanski's party has
OL,9,Fnever polled above 10% in a by-
OL,10,Felection before. They now have their
OL,11,Ffifth MP, their first in the north of
OL,12,FEngland. And in a seat which was 127th
OL,13,Fon their target list.
OL,15,FReform UK's Matt Goodwin says his
OL,16,Fparty has "embarrassed Labour in one
OL,17,Fof their strongest seats", and that
OL,18,Fcoming second is proof they have
OL,19,Fappeal beyond former Conservative
OL,20,Fareas and coastal towns.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772186488
OL,3,C'Worst nightmare' for government as
OL,4,CGreens secure first ever by-election
OL,5,Cvictory
OL,7,FReform UK has also been pointing to
OL,8,Fconcerns from independent election
OL,9,Fobservers of so-called 'family voting'
OL,10,F- an illegal practice where two voters
OL,11,Fuse one polling booth at the same time.
OL,13,FBut it is the party that came third
OL,14,Fwho will be the focus over the next
OL,15,Ffew hours and days. Labour MPs have
OL,16,Fbeen telling me darkly for weeks that
OL,17,Fof all the options, a Green victory
OL,18,Fwould be their "worst nightmare", the
OL,19,Fmost "catastrophic".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
