PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772186488
OL,3,C'Worst nightmare' for government as
OL,4,CGreens secure first ever by-election
OL,5,Cvictory
OL,7,FWhy? Because all the Labour fire in
OL,8,Fthis campaign - and indeed over the
OL,9,Flast year - has been concentrated on
OL,10,FNigel Farage.
OL,12,FThis morning's result blows a hole in
OL,13,Fthe key argument that only Labour can
OL,14,Fbeat Reform, and shows voters who want
OL,15,Fto vote tactically that going Green is
OL,16,Fnot a wasted vote.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772186488
OL,3,C'Worst nightmare' for government as
OL,4,CGreens secure first ever by-election
OL,5,Cvictory
OL,7,FLabour's chair Anna Turley has called
OL,8,Fthe result "disappointing", saying in
OL,9,Fa statement: "We have had thousands of
OL,10,Fconversations over the last few weeks
OL,11,Fand we know the majority of voters
OL,12,Fhere did not want the poisonous
OL,13,Fpolitics of Nigel Farage and Reform. "
OL,15,FHannah Spencer addresses the crowd as
OL,16,Fshe is announced as the new MP for
OL,17,FGorton and Denton.
OL,26,@qD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
