FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772186488
OL,3,C'Worst nightmare' for government as
OL,4,CGreens secure first ever by-election
OL,5,Cvictory
OL,7,FBut among hundreds of Labour MPs
OL,8,Fsitting on much smaller majorities,
OL,9,Fthere will surely be calls for Labour
OL,10,Fto change tack.
OL,12,FAnd then there will be the inevitable
OL,13,Fquestions about whether Greater
OL,14,FManchester Mayor Andy Burnham could
OL,15,Fhave won here if Keir Starmer had
OL,16,Fallowed him stand. It was less than
OL,17,Ftwo years ago that Burnham beat the
OL,18,Fnow Green MP Hannah Spencer to the
OL,19,FGreater Manchester mayoralty by
OL,20,F375,000 votes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772186488
OL,3,C'Worst nightmare' for government as
OL,4,CGreens secure first ever by-election
OL,5,Cvictory
OL,7,FAnd what about the pressure on Keir
OL,8,FStarmer? When Labour in opposition
OL,9,Flost a crucial by-election in
OL,10,FHartlepool, Starmer reportedly had to
OL,11,Fbe talked out of resigning. Labour's
OL,12,FDeputy Leader Lucy Powell was
OL,13,Finsisting earlier in the night that
OL,14,Fthere would be no leadership vacancy.
OL,15,FBut there is still a very dangerous
OL,16,Fset of local and devolved elections to
OL,17,Fcome in May.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772186488
OL,3,C'Worst nightmare' for government as
OL,4,CGreens secure first ever by-election
OL,5,Cvictory
OL,7,FThe challenge for Labour is that they
OL,8,Fwon in 2024 on a one-word promise. But
OL,9,Fjust 18 months later, the clear
OL,10,Fmessage from voters at this by-
OL,11,Felection is that they want 'change'
OL,12,Fagain. And this time, they're looking
OL,13,Fto the smaller parties to deliver it.
OL,15,FYou can hear Talking Politics wherever
OL,16,Fyou get your podcasts, including Apple
OL,17,FPodcasts and Spotify, and watch every
OL,18,Fepisode on YouTube and ITVX.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
